107
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:46,800
[SPEAKER_00] To je to, čovjek migrira.

108
00:07:47,199 --> 00:07:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Čovjek migrira.

109
00:07:48,959 --> 00:07:52,079
