1090
01:34:13,439 --> 01:34:14,239
[SPEAKER_03] Vidite, Tomson je.

1091
01:34:14,720 --> 01:34:16,560
[SPEAKER_01] Vidite, ljudi stvaraju.

1092
01:34:17,760 --> 01:34:21,279
[SPEAKER_02] Vi stvaraju, vi stvaraju, komentirate aktualne TV.

1093
01:34:22,079 --> 01:34:25,600
[SPEAKER_02] Pa ne baš, imamo neki popis, načelno, tema koje treba.

1094
01:34:25,920 --> 01:34:26,239
