1125
01:37:30,800 --> 01:37:34,319
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, jedni i drugi sebi ne mogu dopustiti.

1126
01:37:34,880 --> 01:37:36,720
[SPEAKER_01] To je donekle fanatizam, jel tako?

1127
01:37:37,279 --> 01:37:46,239
